ata.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TNDM/111%2c%e4%ba%a4%e8%a8%b4%2c213%2c20221031%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TNDM,111,交訴,213,20221031,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"交訴","JNO":"213","JDATE":"20221031","JTITLE":"過失致死"}